PrecisAppointment of the following persons as directors of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Race Relations Foundation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years. (YVON FONTAINE, of Moncton, New Brunswick; FO NIEMI, of Montreal, Quebec; SUBHAS RAMCHARAN, of Tecumseh, Ontario; PANA MERCHANT, of Regina, Saskatchewan; ANN D.
